{
  "stem": "935.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I didn't even know whether they were Jewish or whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they were looking for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They came around 12 o'clock at a time when even big Nazis weren't allowed on the street anymore.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know, because she said, this must be a drunk who's, you know, ringing the doorbell.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It wasn't a drunk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were looking for me-- three Nazis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they tried to get up there, and they were that close to the door.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that's when I knew I could never, never sit in a room and hide out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I'd go mad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I'd go absolutely mad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The feeling of total helplessness.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You sit there and you just wait for them to break down the door and get you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It's-- it's incredible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I mean, even if you run, you can't go anywhere but run.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I heard them step by step.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I heard them cursing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "One broke a leg, I hope.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Fell down the stairs and with the flashlight and-- and-- and screaming, I have enough.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Chasing Jews every night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I'm going home!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Dutch.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They were Dutch.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And it took forever for them to-- you could-- you could hear them breathe outside the door.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And you were sitting there like a-- in a shooting gallery.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "A duck in a shooting gallery.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, your heart stops.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think there are these seconds when you make up your mind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do you really want to sit out the war in a chair in an attic?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can you do this without going mad?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know what it takes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I knew I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
